1. Create a new blog
    RequestUrl: http://127.0.0.1:8000/blog/create/ 

2. Create a user
    RequestUrl: http://127.0.0.1:8000/user/create/

3. Register a user to a blog
    RequestUrl: http://127.0.0.1:8000/blog/:blog_id/user/:user_id

4. Add post to blog
    RequestUrl: http://127.0.0.1:8000/post/add/

5. Add comment to post
    RequestUrl: http://127.0.0.1:8000/comment/add/

6. View all blogs
    RequestUrl: http://127.0.0.1:8000/blogs/list/

7. View a blog's details
    RequestUrl: http://127.0.0.1:8000/blog/:blog_id/detail/

8. View a blog's users
    RequestUrl: http://127.0.0.1:8000/blog/:blog_id/users/

9. View a blog's posts
    RequestUrl: http://127.0.0.1:8000/blog/:blog_id/posts/

10. View user's posts
    RequestUrl: http://127.0.0.1:8000/user/:user_id/posts

11. View user's comments 
    RequestUrl: http://127.0.0.1:8000/user/:user_id/comments

12. Edit post
    RequestUrl: http://127.0.0.1:8000/post/:post_id/update

13. Edit comment
    RequestUrl: http://127.0.0.1:8000/comment/:comment_id/update

14. Delete post
    RequestUrl: http://127.0.0.1:8000/post/:post_id/delete

15. Delete comment
    RequestUrl: http://127.0.0.1:8000/comment/:comment_id/delete
    
16. Edit user's info
    RequestUrl: http://127.0.0.1:8000/user/:user_id/update
